3FE87C02.Line5.11E7B7: This is not the only place faith lives! The Light touches everywhere but here. Please, come with me back to Kehjistan.

675D1890.Line3.1264E5: I took an oath. I can’t just abandon my faith because it got hard to keep it.

8EE1287E.Line1.11E7B7: Look around us. Everything rotting. There’s no future here, my love.
